  "title": "AfterViewInit",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/AfterViewInit\", \"name\": \"AfterViewInit\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/interface/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L176-L203\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/8.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/interface/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L176-L203\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"afterviewinit\">AfterViewInit<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#afterviewinit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>A lifecycle hook that is called after Angular has fully initialized\na component's view.\nDefine an <code><a href=\"api/forms/NgForm#ngAfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngAfterViewInit()</a></code> method to handle any additional initialization tasks.</p>\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterViewInit</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#ngAfterViewInit\"><span class=\"member-name\">ngAfterViewInit</span>(): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <div class=\"descendants class\">\n    <h2 id=\"class-implementations\">Class implementations<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#class-implementations\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n\n<ul>\n  \n    <li>\n      <code><a href=\"api/forms/NgForm\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgForm</a></code>\n      \n\n\n    </li>\n  \n</ul>\n\n\n  </div>\n  \n\n</section>\n  \n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">See also<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/core/OnInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnInit</a></code></p>\n</li>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/core/AfterContentInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterContentInit</a></code></p>\n</li>\n    <li><p><a href=\"guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\">Lifecycle Hooks</a> guide</p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"methods\">Methods<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#methods\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"ngAfterViewInit\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n    <h3 id=\"ngafterviewinit\">\n      ngAfterViewInit()\n      \n    <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#ngafterviewinit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/interface/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L196-L202\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/8.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/interface/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L196-L202\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p>A callback method that is invoked immediately after\nAngular has completed initialization of a component's view.\nIt is invoked only once when the view is instantiated.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  \n\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><span class=\"member-name\">ngAfterViewInit</span>(): void</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h6>\n  <p>There are no parameters.</p>\n\n  \n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h6>\n  <p><code>void</code></p>\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n</div>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>The following snippet shows how a component can implement this interface to\ndefine its own view initialization method.</p>\n<code-example path=\"core/ts/metadata/lifecycle_hooks_spec.ts\" region=\"AfterViewInit\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({selector: 'my-cmp', template: `...`})\nclass MyComponent implements <a href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterViewInit</a> {\n  ngAfterViewInit() {\n    // ...\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/AfterContentInit\n - api/core/ViewChild\n - api/core/ViewChildren\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/testing\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/AfterContentInit\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#afterviewinit\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#class-implementations\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#methods\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#ngAfterViewInit\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#ngafterviewinit\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#see-also\n - api/core/AfterViewInit#usage-notes\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/OnInit\n - api/forms/NgForm\n - api/forms/NgForm#ngAfterViewInit\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/interface/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L176-L203\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/interface/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L196-L202\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/8.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/interface/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L176-L203\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/8.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/interface/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L196-L202\n-->"
